    <h3 id="secMorseCode">Morse Code</h3>
    <p>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morse_code">Morse code</a> is a system of communicating data using short and long pulses (also known as dots and dashes).  Morse code can be encoded using two different symbols representing dots and dashes, and optionally a third symbol to represent letter breaks.  A puzzle can also contain visual representations of Morse in the form of dots and dashes, for example, as stripes or emblems on national flags.
    </p>
