    <h3 id="secSemaphore">Semaphore</h3>
    <p>
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flag_semaphore">Flag semaphore</a>, often called "semaphore" for short, is a flag signaling system in which the alphabet is represented by holding two flags at various angles from the body.  In puzzles, if a data stream consists of compass directions, angles, or lines emanating from a common center, it might be semaphore.
    </p>
